snippet.title: Super C (NES) Playthrough - NintendoComplete
snippet.description:
A playthrough of Konami's 1990 run-and gun shooter for the NES, Super C.

It's a bit too easy compared to Contra, but this NES port of Super Contra (named Probotector 2 in Europe) is a big classic in its own right. It's not a cut-down version of the Japanese release like the original Contra was, the graphics and sound are a huge step up from the original US NES game - gotta love all of those digitzed orchestra hits! - the controls are just as good and reliable, and it's even more disturbing in its imagery. What's not to love here?!

Just remember to always attack aggressively!

______
